274
00:15:48,583 --> 00:15:50,458
who is that guy?

275
00:15:51,083 --> 00:15:52,666
-[sighs]
-[Win] He said

276
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:55,375
you have to find out yourself.

277
00:15:55,833 --> 00:15:58,458
[May] Okay, goodbye world.

278
00:15:59,125 --> 00:16:00,291
