from the office.

293
00:16:46,166 --> 00:16:49,125
If there are any decisions 
made after the restructure,

294
00:16:49,291 --> 00:16:51,083
I'll be in touch.

295
00:16:52,333 --> 00:16:55,125
[woman] I can't believe
