[child] Hey, please get my kite for me.

336
00:19:20,916 --> 00:19:22,083
Here.

337
00:19:22,541 --> 00:19:24,083
-Thank you. 
-All right.

338
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:32,916
It's a small world.

339
00:19:33,375 --> 00:19:34,583
What are you doing here?

340
00:19:34,916 --> 00:19:36,416
