♪ Do you know
How great it is to meet you? ♪

1993
02:08:01,833 --> 02:08:06,583
♪ It's you, all because of you ♪

1994
02:08:06,708 --> 02:08:13,625
♪ That my life is memorable ♪

1995
02:08:16,333 --> 02:08:21,125
♪ It's because I've met you ♪

