♪ Thank all the stories ♪

1999
02:08:37,250 --> 02:08:39,416
♪ And all the reasons ♪

2000
02:08:42,125 --> 02:08:43,791
[whoops]

2001
02:08:43,875 --> 02:08:48,666
♪ You, my love ♪

2002
